From: Arturo Marti Carvajal <amarti@cid.cid.ve>

I am performing a review about bleeding in patients with dengue in order to
update the pathophysiology and [case] management. If you have or know any
good report (with solid evidence), please send it to me at my mailing
address below. Of course, I would welcome any suggests, comments,
recommendations [via] e-mail.
